## 🌟 Key Features
| Feature          | Emoji | Description                          |
|------------------|-------|--------------------------------------|
| API Integration  | 🌐    | Fetch real book data from Google API 
| Clean UI         | 🎨    | Card-based layout with hover effects |
| Mobile-Friendly  | 📱    | Responsive grid and typography       |

